Class InternalHttpSession

java.lang.Object
  org.dspace.services.sessions.model.InternalHttpSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.servlet.http.HttpSession
public final class InternalHttpSession
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpSession

This is a special HTTP session object that stands in for a real one when sessions are not initiated or associated by HTTP requests.
